test_addition()[source]

Tests addition method of ComplexNumber class

Requirements:

1- The method should return an object of ComplexNumber class

2- The attributes of the class should be verified that operation can be executed correctly

2- The method should raise TypeError exception if wrong arguments given

3- The method should raise ValueError exception if no argument given

TestCases:

1- assertIsInstance: to verify returned object’s type

2- assertEqual x2: to verify real and imaginary attributes of the object (algorithm check)

3 and 4- assertRaises x2: to verify parameter types
